Description: LCD display controller for Thermalright USB cooler screens
 Neru Screen Control lets you drive the small USB LCD display built into
 Thermalright CPU coolers directly from Linux — no Windows software required.
 .
 Features include live CPU/GPU metric display with a custom canvas theme
 editor, image/GIF/video playback, a built-in calibration tool, systemd
 user service for background operation, and a system tray icon.
